ition stage to emit score-tree with PerformanceIntent + SectionEnvelope + IntentTag metadata, deterministic from composition seed. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-008 | Define the OSC/SuperCollider event contract that carries full Event metadata including rule_stack provenance through to the synth. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-009 | Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-010 | Build a rule-ablation debugger that re-renders a score with selected rules disabled to localize expressive problems. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-011 | Build the RenderPass framework: ordered rule stack with stable order, per-rule enable flags, per-rule quantity k, and role-filter gating. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-012 | Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-013 | Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-014 | Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-015 | Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ±10%. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-016 | Implement R5 Final Ritardando: Friberg–Sundberg square-root tempo curve over last 20–30% of cadential phrases. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-017 | Implement R6 Punctuation + Breath: lengthen terminal note at phrase boundary and insert breath silence of breath_after_ms. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\