my-claw/sdp/prd-clone-and-home-creation.md:35:| HOMECLONE-007 | Implement install-time mode selection with `standalone` and `federated` as explicit initial modes. | MUST | T1 | - Install manifest stores the initial mode<br/>- Standalone homes do not announce or auto-share<br/>- Federated homes enable discovery and announcement hooks |
my-claw/sdp/prd-clone-and-home-creation.md:36:| HOMECLONE-008 | Implement user-settable secret policy during unattended and clone install. The operator must be able to choose between copying source secrets and provisioning fresh secrets. | MUST | T1 | - Secret policy is explicit in install config<br/>- Copying secrets is optional, not implicit<br/>- Fresh-secret installs boot without source-secret leakage |
